#: src/Admin/Settings.php:98
msgid "Swatch replaces the default WooCommerce variation selects with accessible colour or label swatches. Set a colour or label per attribute term on the global attribute screens (Products → Attributes → Configure terms), then tune the look here. Hover a “?” for a quick explanation."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:106
msgid "General"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:111
msgid "Enable swatches"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:112
msgid "Master switch. When off, WooCommerce shows its standard dropdowns everywhere and no swatch assets are loaded."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:124
msgid "Replace variation dropdowns with swatches on single product pages."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:130
msgid "Default swatch type"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:131
msgid "Used for any attribute you have not given an explicit type. “Colour” shows colour dots (needs a colour set per term); “Button” shows the term name as a pill — the safe choice for sizes, materials and anything without a colour."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:139
msgid "Attributes with no colours configured automatically fall back to the dropdown, so this is safe to leave on “Colour”."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:147
msgid "Appearance"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:152
msgid "Colour swatch shape"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:153
msgid "Shape of colour swatches. Button/label swatches are always pill-shaped."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:158
msgid "Circle"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:159
msgid "Square"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:164
msgid "Swatch size (px)"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:164
msgid "Height of each swatch in pixels (20–80)."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:164
msgid "The visible height of each swatch. Colour swatches are square/round at this size; button swatches use it as their height."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:165
msgid "Button min width (px)"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:165
msgid "Minimum width of button/label swatches (0–200)."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:165
msgid "Keeps short labels (like “S” or “XL”) from looking cramped. Set 0 to size purely to the text."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:169
msgid "Tooltip"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:170
msgid "Shows the term name in a native tooltip on hover and focus. The name is always available to screen readers regardless of this setting."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:182
msgid "Show the term name as a tooltip on hover/focus."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:188
msgid "Selected value label"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:189
msgid "Prints the chosen value (e.g. “Red”) next to the swatches, updated as the shopper selects. Handy for colour swatches where the dot alone is not enough."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:201
msgid "Show the selected value beside the swatches."
msgstr ""

